2.4","text":"And his host, and those that were numbered of them, were threescore and fourteen thousand and six hundred.","year":-1490},{"id":"recQoZ8SZwa6bdLeE","ref":"Num.2.5","text":"And those that do pitch next unto him shall be the tribe of Issachar: and Nethaneel the son of Zuar shall be captain of the children of Issachar.","year":-1490},{"id":"reci9xCRwxwJr831N","ref":"Num.2.6","text":"And his host, and those that were numbered thereof, were fifty and four thousand and four hundred.","year":-1490},{"id":"rec2wMf1rraCuzaOF","ref":"Num.2.7","text":"Then the tribe of Zebulun: and Eliab the son of Helon shall be captain of the children of Zebulun.","year":-1490},{"id":"rec7rRqDynR2YuY3j","ref":"Num.2.8","text":"And his host, and those that were numbered thereof, were fifty and seven thousand and four hundred.","year":-1490}]}
